title: The Collected Uber (Avatar|2013->|Digital-HR|Empire)
description:
" [... I]t's 'Uber'. There's no way that our origin stories were going to
      be as comfortable and life-affirming as your family getting gunned down.

      [...] You can tell you're walking on prickly ground when the story you
      feel most comfortable with involves [the carpet-bombing of] Dresden. " 

        --  Author's notes, Uber Special #1


Overview:  <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%9Cber_%28comics%29" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%9Cber_%28comics%29</a>
